----------------------------------------------------------------------------

RESPONSIBLE USE NOTICE

The MCPHunt framework and datasets are intended for research and defensive
evaluation of Model Context Protocol (MCP) agent safety. They MUST NOT be
used to:

- Develop or distribute working exploits against deployed MCP systems
- Probe production MCP servers without explicit authorization
- Generate misleading safety-evaluation results for marketing or audit fraud
- Train models to evade compositional safety checks

The synthetic nature of the datasets is a deliberate safeguard. Users should
treat the framework as a measurement instrument, not as an attack toolkit.
